      <h2>Best Travel Credit Cards in India</h2>
      <p>Travel credit cards are designed for frequent flyers and globetrotters who want to maximise value from their travel spending. These cards earn air miles or travel reward points on every transaction, offer complimentary airport lounge access, include comprehensive travel insurance, and provide preferential forex rates for international transactions. The right travel card can save you ₹30,000-₹1,00,000+ per year in travel benefits alone.</p>
      <p>India's leading travel cards from HDFC, Axis, ICICI, and American Express offer perks like Priority Pass memberships, airline loyalty program transfers, hotel upgrade vouchers, and dedicated travel concierge services. Whether you fly 4 times a year or 40, there's a travel card that fits your frequency and budget.</p>

      <h2>Key Features of Travel Credit Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Airport Lounge Access:</strong> 4-12+ complimentary domestic and international lounge visits per year via Priority Pass or Dreamfolks</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Air Miles Earning:</strong> Earn 2-10 air miles per ₹100 spent, with accelerated earning on airline and travel bookings</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Travel Insurance:</strong> Air accident cover up to ₹1 crore, trip cancellation protection, lost baggage reimbursement</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Low Forex Markup:</strong> Many travel cards charge 1.5-2% forex markup compared to 3.5% on regular cards</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Airline Program Transfers:</strong> Transfer reward points to Singapore Airlines, Air India, Vistara, and other loyalty programs</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Concierge Services:</strong> 24/7 travel concierge for flight bookings, hotel reservations, and itinerary planning</li>
      </ul>

